*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Media
*.mp4
*.mp3
*.avi

# Large files
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# Documentation
*.md
*.txt

# Configuration
*.config.js
*.config.ts

# Development
*.dev
*.test

# Production
*.prod
*.production

# Security
*.key
*.pem
*.crt

